  "topic": "Percent Yield",
  "question": "What is percent yield?",
  "options": {
    "A": "(Theoretical yield / Actual yield) \u00d7 100%",
    "B": "(Actual yield / Theoretical yield) \u00d7 100%",
    "C": "(Actual mass / Molar mass) \u00d7 100%",
    "D": "(Moles / Volume) \u00d7 100%"
  },
  "answer": "B",
  "explanation": "Percent yield = (actual yield / theoretical yield) \u00d7 100%. It shows efficiency of a reaction."
}